msg: mod_mem_cache needs cache_hash.lo in order to link properly

author: jwoolley
msg: mod_mem_cache.c:251: too many arguments to function `cache_hash_first'

author: stoddard
msg: Introduce a dedicated cache hash adt that does not rely on pools. This
cures a storage leak when garbage collecting expired entries out of the
hash table. cache_hash is just apr_hash with some of the function removed
and reimplemented to use malloc/free in place of apr_pool calls.
